 Indian girl, Pooja Khan was scold by her parents for wearing short clothes after she was bitten by mosquito. According to reports, Pooja was bitten by mosquito in school and when she asked her parents to bring mosquito killer or a net, they refused and scolded her for wearing short clothes and leaving so much skin exposed for the mosquito to come and attack. Meanwhile schools have decided to bring an order to regulate the length of clothes as the rainy season is approaching and the mosquito menace is well known.